      "section_id": "para_42",
      "heading": "WATER SUPPLY (FEDERAL TERRITORY OF\nKUALA LUMPUR) ACT 1998",
      "content": "WATER SUPPLY (FEDERAL TERRITORY OF\nKUALA LUMPUR) ACT 1998",
