    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_43",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "An Act to provide for the law relating to the supply and distribution\nof water in the Federal Territory of Kuala Lumpur and for matters\nincidental to it.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_44",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "[Federal Territory of Kuala Lumpur—\n29 April 2004, P.U. (B) 223/2004;\n*Federal Territory of Putrajaya—\n30 April 2004, P.U (A) 142/2004]",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_45",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "BE IT ENACTED by the Seri Paduka Baginda Yang di-Pertuan\nAgong with the advice and consent of the Dewan Negara and Dewan\nRakyat in Parliament assembled, and by  the authority of the same,\nas follows:",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_46",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Short title",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_47",
      "heading": "1. This Act may be cited as the Water Supply (Federal Territory of\nKuala Lumpur) Act 1998.",
      "content": "1. This Act may be cited as the Water Supply (Federal Territory of\nKuala Lumpur) Act 1998.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_48",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Law applicable to Federal Territory of Kuala Lumpur",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_49",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "2. (1) The law relating to the supply and distribution of water in the\nState  of  Selangor  shall  apply  to  the  Federal  Territory  of  Kuala\nLumpur but with the necessary modifications, as the context may\nrequire.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_50",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(2) Notwithstanding subsection (1), the Minister may by order\nmake such modifications as may be necessary to any provision of the\nlaw  referred  to  in  subsection  (1)  for  the  purpose  of  removing\ndifficulties  in  its  application  to  the  Federal  Territory  of  Kuala\nLumpur.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_51",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "*NOTE—In its application to the Federal Territory of Putrajaya–see the Federal Territory of Putrajaya\n(Extension  and  Modification  of  Water  Supply  (Federal  Territory  of  Kuala  Lumpur)\nAct 1998) Order 2004 [P.U. (A) 142/2004].",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_52",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "6",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_53",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Laws of Malaysia",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_54",
      "heading": "ACT 581",
      "content": "ACT 581",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_55",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Authority responsible for Federal Territory of Kuala Lumpur\nin water matters",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_56",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "3. (1) The authority responsible for the supply and distribution of\nwater  in  the  State  of  Selangor  shall  exercise,  on  behalf  of  the\nGovernment of the Federation, the powers and functions under the\nlaw applicable to the Federal Territory of Kuala Lumpur on matters\nrelating  to  the  supply  and  distribution  of  water  in  the  Federal\nTerritory of Kuala Lumpur.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_57",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(2) Nothing in subsection (1) shall preclude the Government of\nthe Federation from exercising on its own behalf the powers and\nfunctions relating to the supply and distribution of water under the\nlaw applicable to the Federal Territory of Kuala Lumpur.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_58",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Repeal",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_59",
      "heading": "4. (1) The Water Supply Enactment [F.M.S. Cap. 203] shall cease\nto apply in the Federal Territory of Kuala Lumpur.",
      "content": "4. (1) The Water Supply Enactment [F.M.S. Cap. 203] shall cease\nto apply in the Federal Territory of Kuala Lumpur.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_60",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(2) The Federal Territory (Water Supply Enactment) Order 1974",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_61",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "[P.U. (A) 153/1974] is revoked.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_62",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(3) Subsidiary legislation made under the Water Supply Enactment\nand in force in the Federal Territory of Kuala Lumpur shall continue\nto  be  in  force  until  revoked,  amended  or  replaced  by  subsidiary\nlegislation made in respect of the Federal Territory of Kuala Lumpur\nunder the law relating to the supply and distribution of water in the\nFederal Territory of Kuala Lumpur.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
